No, I really think I do.

1439
01:45:19,949 --> 01:45:21,826
Your funeral.

1440
01:45:24,997 --> 01:45:26,997
And why don't I
want to be doing it?

1441
01:45:27,040 --> 01:45:28,708
Oh, because...

1442
01:45:29,709 --> 01:45:32,044
Because the HMS Dauntless,

1443
01:45:32,128 --> 01:45:34,546
the pride of the Royal Navy,

1444
