What Mr Sparrow said we should do?

1453
01:46:06,912 --> 01:46:08,414
With the cannons and all?

1454
01:46:08,499 --> 01:46:11,541
Because it was Mr
Sparrow who said it.

1455
01:46:14,169 --> 01:46:16,755
You think he wasn't
telling the truth?

1456
01:46:16,839 --> 01:46:18,716
Just hear me out, mate.

1457
01:46:18,801 --> 01:46:20,603
You order your men
to row out to the

1458
01:46:20,604 --> 01:46:22,552
Dauntless, they do
what they do best...

1459
01:46:23,639 --> 01:46:25,722
Robert's your uncle, Fanny's your

1460
