aunt. There you
are with two ships.

1461
01:46:28,142 --> 01:46:30,560
The makings of your
very own fleet.

1462
01:46:30,645 --> 01:46:32,464
Because, you'll take
the grandest as

1463
01:46:32,465 --> 01:46:34,232
your flagship, and who's to argue?

1464
01:46:34,316 --> 01:46:35,732
But what of the Pearl?

1465
01:46:37,359 --> 01:46:38,695
Name me captain.

1466
01:46:38,737 --> 01:46:40,393
I'll sail under your colours, I'll

1467
01:46:40,394 --> 01:46:42,196
give you ten percent
of me plunder,

1468
01:46:42,239 --> 01:46:44,448
and you'll get to
introduce yourself as...

1469
01:46:45,033 --> 01:46:47,911
Commodore Barbossa.

1470
01:46:47,954 --> 01:46:49,037
Savvy?

1471
01:46:49,080 --> 01:46:51,289
I suppose, in exchange, you'll be

1472
01:46:51,373 --> 01:46:53,264
